Name: Cliché - Critical Change
About the game: When a game is rated M for MANLY! Cliché… A phrase that is overused… It betrays a lack of original thought… Has the time come for a change? A critical change! Raise Muki, a muscular girl with the heart of a maiden in any way you want! Guide her so she can be with her beloved prince! Will things go horribly wrong, or horribly right? It is all up to you! Comedy, Fantasy & Adventure Raising Sim, Puzzle & Visual Novel 9+ Endings & Unlockable Gallery Rated Everyone
